snippet.title: JUDGEMENT SILVERSWORD - Resurrection - Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy now: http://store.steampowered.com/app/278510

Two classic Wonderswan shooting games, now on PC! Battle the mysterious Judges in Judgement Silversword. Cardinal Sins is a score trial marathon, based on the theme of the Seven Deadly Sins. Will you face final Judgement?

JUDGEMENT SILVERSWORD / CARDINAL SINS
